Class IdentificationSet<X>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<X>
        • org.intellimate.izou.util.IdentificationSet<X>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Iterable<X>, Collection<X>, Set<X>, Identifiable

    public class IdentificationSet<X>
extends AbstractSet<X>
implements Set<X>, Cloneable, Identifiable
    It has the same Properties as an normal HashSet, but (optionally) keeps an Identification for every object to identify its source.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Leander Kurscheidt
